handType.title: Hand Type
handType.description: Any is either hand and Neither is when the pad has no left/right identity

priority.title: Priority
priority.description: The nth hand of this type that is connected. E.g. A priority of 2 with a hand type of Left would be 3rd left hand that is connected to the system

layer.title: Layer
layer.description: Has to be between a value of 3 and 14. 3 being the highest priority

screenMaterial.title: Screen Material
screenMaterial.description: The screen material of the TV that displays the video texture.

playEvent.title: Play Event
playEvent.description: Set the TV screen material emissive map on this event.

startTime.title: Start Time (Secs)
startTime.description: Start the path from a specific point in time

soundSlotName.title: Sound Slot Name
soundSlotName.description: Name of slot to play on Hifi

camera.description: Optional, assign a camera entity, otherwise one is created

power.description: Adjusts the speed of player movement

startTime.title: Start Time (Secs)
startTime.description: Start the path from a specific point in time

fadeDropOff.title: Fade Drop Off
fadeDropOff.description: When to start fading out hotspot relative to the camera direction. 1 for when hotspot is directly inline with the camera. 0 for never.

compatibleTag.title: Compatible Tag
compatibleTag.description: Tag that this object can interact with

presetEntity.title: Preset Entity
presetEntity.description: Entity to be attached to this on start

keepUpdating.title: Keep Updating
keepUpdating.description: Update the shape data every frame (only toggle if the entity moves as can be expensive)

childOfActualEntity.title: Child Of Actual Entity
childOfActualEntity.description: Tick if the shape is a child of the actual entity object

fakeElbowOffset.title: Fake Elbow Offset
fakeElbowOffset.description: Local offset between the camera and a simulated fake right elbow. Used for 3DOF controllers like the Daydream

fakeWristOffset.title: Fake Wrist Offset
fakeWristOffset.description: Local offset between the fake elbow and the fake wrist. Used for 3DOF controllers like the Daydream

video.title: Video
video.description: MP4 video asset to play back on this video texture.

playEvent.title: Play Event
playEvent.description: Event that is fired as soon as the video texture is ready to play.
